query:
SELECT content_hash
                    FROM library_unit_build
                    WHERE
                        package_id = $1
                        AND target = $2
                        AND library_crate_compilation_unit_hash = $3
                        AND COALESCE(build_script_compilation_unit_hash, '') = COALESCE($4, '')
                        AND COALESCE(build_script_execution_unit_hash, '') = COALESCE($5, '')
